research/history/logs/agent_round_0013.stdout.log:51:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"The `signum` learning-rate sweep has now mapped a narrow optimum region around `1.7e-3` to `1.75e-3`, with no clear additional gain from pushing LR higher. This round changes only the loss-shaping axis by lowering `AUXK_ALPHA` from the current implicit baseline `0.03125` to `0.015625` while keeping `topk/signum/K128/EF12/LR=1.7e-3` fixed, to test whether a weaker auxiliary dead-feature pressure improves late-stage reconstruction once the main LR regime is already near its peak.","summary":"Stay on the `topk` mainline and move to the next recipe axis after LR refinement: keep `ARCHITECTURE=topk`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, and `LR=1.7e-3` fixed, and reduce `AUXK_ALPHA` to `0.015625` to answer whether lighter auxiliary regularization yields a better training curve and lower final FVU.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This keeps the active family unchanged and modifies only one non-core recipe variable, which fits the single-variable rule and avoids the optimizer-callback policy trap encountered earlier. The risk is that lowering `AUXK_ALPHA` may weaken dead-feature management and hurt utilization, but at this stage the more important question is whether the current LR-tuned regime is now over-regularized in reconstruction terms.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.7e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.015625"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["The signum LR sweep suggests the practical optimum is near `1.7e-3`; pushing to `1.75e-3` did not yield a meaningful additional gain.","With LR mostly mapped, the next clean single-variable question is whether current loss shaping is slightly over-constraining reconstruction.","Judge this round by full curve shape plus terminal FVU: if lower `AUXK_ALPHA` improves late descent without obvious instability, the mainline recipe should shift on the loss axis rather than continuing micro-LR sweeps."],"next_hypotheses":["If `AUXK_ALPHA=0.015625` improves FVU and keeps the curve smooth, continue tuning aux loss strength within the same topk recipe.","If the lower aux weight hurts stability or feature health without improving reconstruction, revert to `0.03125` and treat LR-tuned signum as the current clean anchor.","If the effect is neutral, the topk mainline may be recipe-saturated at K=128 and the next useful step will be a K move once policy order permits."],"primary_variable":"other_param"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0224.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"96"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r u_r + Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是静态 trunk 向量库、{b_i} 是静态 residual 向量库；在线侧只计算 trunk 系数 β_r 与 residual 稀疏系数 α_i，再执行 trunk 查表 + residual 查表 + 加权求和，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。r223 已确认 `topk@EF1,K248` 的 recipe 轴继续向上推 LR 只带来更差 FVU 和明显更差吞吐，说明当前 <0.5x 最强 topk 锚点已基本饱和；同时 r221 说明直接压 `TRUNK_RANK` 会破坏 lowrank_factorized_residual 的 trunk 表达。基于 r210 这个高质量参考点，本轮严格只改一个 env 参数 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96`，保留 `K=64, EF=1, signum, LR=3e-3` 与完整 trunk 分支不变，用更短的 factorized scorer 链路替代默认较宽隐藏层，测试是否能把该 family 的 total_cost 从 0.69x 压到约 0.48x，同时尽量保留显著优于同成本 topk 的 FVU。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 在约 0.48x 成本下仍明显优于 `topk@0.48x` 的 FVU=0.1483，且训练吞吐没有像 r221 那样恶化，则下一轮相对本轮继续单变量下探到 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=64`，寻找更低成本拐点。","如果 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 的 FVU 明显退化到接近或差于同成本 topk，则说明该 family 的优势主要来自更宽 scorer 而非 trunk 本身；下一轮应关闭这条 scorer 压缩线，转向新的低成本 family。","如果该配置质量接近 r210 但系统代价明显更差，则保留其为解释性对照，不继续把该 family 作为 <0.5x 主战场。"],"notes_to_memory":["r223 给出明确负面信号：`topk@EF1,K248` 的向上 LR 分支已不值得继续，后续应把注意力从 topk recipe 清洗转回新低成本结构。","本地 `selection_cost_estimate()` 显示 `lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1,FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 的 combined_ratio 约为 0.48x，已进入当前重点搜索区间，而不需要再次牺牲 trunk。","与压 `TRUNK_RANK` 不同，压 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 只缩短 factorized scorer 链路，保留 trunk 静态库的容量，更符合当前“降低选择成本但不破坏导出结构”的目标。"],"reference_round":210,"self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则：相对有效参考轮 r210 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，family、K、EF、optimizer、LR 及其他结构参数全部不变。选择 96 而不是 128，是因为 128 只会把总成本压到约 0.50x 边界，仍不够明确进入当前主目标区；选择 96 而不是更激进的 64，则是为了先做最小但有效的 scorer 压缩，尽量保留 r210 已证明存在的质量优势。","summary":"相对 r210 的 `lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1` 做一次严格 param_only 低成本压缩，仅设置 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96`，验证保留完整 trunk 时，缩短 factorized scorer 链路能否把该 family 推入 `<0.5x` Pareto 主前沿。","touched_files":[]}
