research/history/round_summaries/round_0004.json:106:    "description": "\u7ee7\u7eed\u56f4\u7ed5 topk \u4e3b\u7ebf\u63a8\u8fdb\uff0c\u4e0d\u5f00\u65b0 family\uff0c\u4e0d\u6362\u4f18\u5316\u5668\uff0c\u4e0d\u52a8 K\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u53d8\u91cf\u662f\u5b66\u4e60\u7387\uff1a\u4ece 1e-3 \u5c0f\u5e45\u4e0a\u8c03\u5230 1.2e-3\uff0c\u56de\u7b54\u201csignum+topk \u7684\u66f4\u4f18 LR \u662f\u5426\u5728 1e-3 \u4e4b\u4e0a\u201d\u8fd9\u4e2a\u5355\u4e00\u95ee\u9898\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0022.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 21 showed that `topk/signum/LR=1.6e-3/EF=12` at `K=96` is a promising high-quality reduced-cost point: its curve kept descending smoothly through the late phase, and both `dead_pct` and `auxk` stayed very low. This round changes only the loss-shaping axis, lowering `AUXK_ALPHA` from `0.03125` to `0.015625` while keeping the `K=96` recipe fixed, to answer whether the new near-anchor deployment point is slightly over-regularized and can recover a bit more reconstruction quality without destabilizing training.","summary":"Run a single loss-axis test on the newly validated `K=96` topk point: keep `ARCHITECTURE=topk`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, `K=96`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and reduce `AUXK_ALPHA` to `0.015625` to see whether weaker auxiliary pressure improves the high-quality reduced-cost recipe.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays on the active `topk` family, changes exactly one primary variable (`other_param` via `AUXK_ALPHA`), respects the fixed `EF=12` rule, and follows directly from the observed `K=96` curve shape. The main risk is that the gain may be small, but `K=96` is now the most promising reduced-cost point and its very low dead-feature pressure makes a clean over-regularization check more justified than continuing to remap K.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"96"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.015625"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 21 established `K=96` as a strong high-quality reduced-cost point: late-phase FVU kept descending smoothly and both `dead_pct` and `auxk` remained near zero.","Because `K=96` is not capacity-stressed like the low-K regime, it is a better place than `K=8` or `K=16` to test whether the current auxiliary dead-feature pressure is slightly too strong.","This round returns from K mapping to recipe tuning, while still staying inside the same family and on a deployment-relevant point rather than retreating all the way to the K128 anchor."],"next_hypotheses":["If lower `AUXK_ALPHA` improves `K=96`, keep the same K fixed and continue recipe refinement there before revisiting other K values.","If lower `AUXK_ALPHA` does not help, treat the current `K=96/signum/LR=1.6e-3` recipe as close to saturated and move to another single recipe axis.","If reducing `AUXK_ALPHA` hurts stability or quality, the current auxiliary pressure is likely already appropriate for this near-anchor reduced-cost point."],"primary_variable":"other_param"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0224.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"96"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r u_r + Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是静态 trunk 向量库、{b_i} 是静态 residual 向量库；在线侧只计算 trunk 系数 β_r 与 residual 稀疏系数 α_i，再执行 trunk 查表 + residual 查表 + 加权求和，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。r223 已确认 `topk@EF1,K248` 的 recipe 轴继续向上推 LR 只带来更差 FVU 和明显更差吞吐，说明当前 <0.5x 最强 topk 锚点已基本饱和；同时 r221 说明直接压 `TRUNK_RANK` 会破坏 lowrank_factorized_residual 的 trunk 表达。基于 r210 这个高质量参考点，本轮严格只改一个 env 参数 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96`，保留 `K=64, EF=1, signum, LR=3e-3` 与完整 trunk 分支不变，用更短的 factorized scorer 链路替代默认较宽隐藏层，测试是否能把该 family 的 total_cost 从 0.69x 压到约 0.48x，同时尽量保留显著优于同成本 topk 的 FVU。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 在约 0.48x 成本下仍明显优于 `topk@0.48x` 的 FVU=0.1483，且训练吞吐没有像 r221 那样恶化，则下一轮相对本轮继续单变量下探到 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=64`，寻找更低成本拐点。","如果 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 的 FVU 明显退化到接近或差于同成本 topk，则说明该 family 的优势主要来自更宽 scorer 而非 trunk 本身；下一轮应关闭这条 scorer 压缩线，转向新的低成本 family。","如果该配置质量接近 r210 但系统代价明显更差，则保留其为解释性对照，不继续把该 family 作为 <0.5x 主战场。"],"notes_to_memory":["r223 给出明确负面信号：`topk@EF1,K248` 的向上 LR 分支已不值得继续，后续应把注意力从 topk recipe 清洗转回新低成本结构。","本地 `selection_cost_estimate()` 显示 `lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1,FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 的 combined_ratio 约为 0.48x，已进入当前重点搜索区间，而不需要再次牺牲 trunk。","与压 `TRUNK_RANK` 不同，压 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 只缩短 factorized scorer 链路，保留 trunk 静态库的容量，更符合当前“降低选择成本但不破坏导出结构”的目标。"],"reference_round":210,"self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则：相对有效参考轮 r210 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，family、K、EF、optimizer、LR 及其他结构参数全部不变。选择 96 而不是 128，是因为 128 只会把总成本压到约 0.50x 边界，仍不够明确进入当前主目标区；选择 96 而不是更激进的 64，则是为了先做最小但有效的 scorer 压缩，尽量保留 r210 已证明存在的质量优势。","summary":"相对 r210 的 `lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1` 做一次严格 param_only 低成本压缩，仅设置 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96`，验证保留完整 trunk 时，缩短 factorized scorer 链路能否把该 family 推入 `<0.5x` Pareto 主前沿。","touched_files":[]}
