research/history/logs/agent_action_0112.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.4e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j；其中 low-rank trunk、soft codebook、两阶段 residual 都是静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，因此该 family 属于扩展兼容。单主变量改为 EXPANSION_FACTOR: 12 -> 2，可把该 family 的 selection_cost 压到约 1.16x h×n，回到 ≤1.5x 硬预算内，同时保留当前主线结构，回答“这个强 backbone 在最低可行 EF 下是否仍能以更低总在线成本给出比 factorized_topk 更好的 FVU/时延权衡”。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 EF=2 已可行且 FVU 仍明显优于 factorized_topk，则下一轮在同 family 上补 clean baseline，检查曲线是否仍在下降。","若 EF=2 曲线形状健康但收敛偏慢，则只调 LR 作为单变量。","若 EF=2 的 FVU 退化过大，则保留该 family 但转向单变量降低 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM 或 TRUNK_RANK，探索 EF=2 下更便宜 scorer 的最优点。"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性：扩展兼容；导出形式为 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","本轮严格遵守单变量原则，只验证 EF 收缩后的成本可行性与低 EF 表达质量。","K 对选择成本几乎无影响，因此保持 K=128，不把成本变化和稀疏预算变化混在一起。"],"primary_variable":"expansion_factor","self_review":"这是当前策略要求下最小且可归因的主线动作：先把主线 family 拉回预算内，再看其低 EF regime 是否仍有竞争力。风险是 EF=2 可能让 FVU 明显恶化，但这正是本轮唯一要回答的问题。","summary":"继续主线 family，不开新架构。用参考配方 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual / K=128 / signum / LR=2.4e-3，仅将 EXPANSION_FACTOR 从 12 降到 2，先验证该扩展兼容结构在 LUTurbo 选择成本预算内的可行 Pareto 点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0170.json:23:    "self_review": "This obeys the single-variable rule by changing only `architecture` and explicitly pinning the current mainline recipe fields. After the recent asymmetric, gated, and jumprelu probes failed to pressure the mainline, the highest-value remaining matched probe is the strongest cheaper parent `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual`: it preserves the same formula class except for removing the second residual stage, stays within the EF=2 budget, and directly tests whether that extra stage is actually earning its cost in the current deployable regime. The main risk is limited novelty because this family is already known historically, but it is still the cleanest remaining architecture-worthiness question under the forced probe policy.",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0219.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"256"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 family: factorized_topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；低秩 factorized scorer 只影响在线打分与选址，不改变 decoder 端仍是单库有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿链路，兼容性为直接兼容。r214-r218 已表明 topk@EF1 沿 K 轴继续加预算仍能改善 FVU，但最近两轮收益已明显变小且总耗时上升到 417s，说明单纯堆 topk 查表预算接近边际收益极限；本轮因此切到更低 encoder 成本的 factorized_topk，并把 K 提到 EF=1 下的满字典 256，测试是否能在总成本仍预计约 0.44x、继续位于 <0.5x 区域的前提下，用更便宜的 selector 换取更高可用 K，从而拿到接近或优于 topk@0.49x 的低开销 FVU。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 factorized_topk@EF1,K256 在 <0.5x 内接近或优于 topk@K248 的 FVU，说明低秩 scorer 路线在极低 EF 下仍值得保留，可继续围绕该 family 做低成本补点。","如果 factorized_topk@EF1,K256 仍明显落后于 topk，说明当前低开销区的关键不在 selector 降本而在表示本身，后续应转向其他兼容 family 而不是继续追 factorized scorer。"],"notes_to_memory":["factorized_topk 的 decoder 形式始终是单静态字典上的有限加权和，属于直接兼容 family；改变 scorer 结构不会破坏 LUTurbo 导出契约。","在 EF=1 下，factorized_topk 的 encoder 成本预计明显低于 topk，因此允许把 K 推到满字典而仍留在 <0.5x 区域；这是当前最有信息量的新 family 低开销 probe。","评估时必须同步检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认更便宜 scorer 是否带来真实系统收益，而不是只看终点 FVU。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮不再继续沿 topk 的 K 轴做更小边际收益的贴边补点，而是用一次新的直接兼容 architecture probe 回答更关键的问题：更便宜的 factorized selector 能否在 <0.5x 区域重新获得竞争力。风险是该 family 在历史低 K 点上偏弱，但当前 EF=1 且 K=256 的 regime 与以往不同，值得单轮验证。","summary":"切换到直接兼容的 factorized_topk family，固定 EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，并把 K 提到 256，测试是否能在仍低于 0.5x 总成本的前提下，用更低 encoder 成本的 selector 获得接近或优于当前 topk 低开销前沿的 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0228.json:7:  "family_name": "jumprelu",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0228.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family: jumprelu\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_i \u03b1_i b_i\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d {b_i} \u6765\u81ea\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff1bJumpReLU \u53ea\u6539\u53d8\u5355\u6837\u672c\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u7684\u9608\u503c\u5316\u652f\u6301\u5f62\u6210\u4e0e\u7cfb\u6570\u8ba1\u7b97\uff0c\u4e0d\u6539\u53d8 decoder \u7aef\u7684\u5355\u5e93\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r227 \u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a env \u53c2\u6570 `K=240`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=jumprelu`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH=0.05`\u3001`JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.02`\u3001`signum`\u3001`LR=0.003` \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5728\u5df2\u7ecf\u4e8e 0.49x \u6210\u672c\u70b9\u4f18\u4e8e topk \u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u8f7b\u5fae\u7f29\u77ed\u67e5\u8868\u94fe\u8def\u540e\u662f\u5426\u4ecd\u80fd\u4fdd\u6301\u5bf9\u540c\u6210\u672c\u90bb\u8fd1 topk \u70b9\u7684\u8d28\u91cf\u4f18\u52bf\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u8865\u51fa `<0.5x` \u533a\u57df\u66f4\u4f4e deployment \u6210\u672c\u4e00\u4fa7\u7684 Pareto \u524d\u6cbf\u3002\u8be5\u6539\u52a8\u53ea\u964d\u4f4e\u90e8\u7f72\u67e5\u8868\u6210\u672c\uff0c\u4e0d\u589e\u52a0 encoder \u6210\u672c\uff0ctotal_cost \u9884\u8ba1\u5c06\u4ece\u7ea6 0.49x \u5c0f\u5e45\u964d\u5230\u7ea6 0.48x\uff0c\u4ecd\u7a33\u5c45\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u6218\u533a\u4e14\u6ee1\u8db3 LUTurbo \u603b\u6210\u672c\u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0228.json:20:    "summary": "\u76f8\u5bf9 r227 \u7684 `jumprelu@EF1,K248,JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH=0.05,JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.02` \u505a\u4e00\u6b21\u4e25\u683c param_only frontier probe\uff0c\u4ec5\u5c06 `K` \u4e0b\u8c03\u5230 `240`\u3002\u76ee\u6807\u662f\u5728\u7565\u964d\u603b\u6210\u672c\u7684\u540c\u65f6\uff0c\u9a8c\u8bc1 jumprelu \u80fd\u5426\u7ee7\u7eed\u538b\u8fc7\u5f53\u524d `topk@0.48x` \u90bb\u8fd1\u70b9\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u8865\u51fa `<0.5x` \u533a\u57df\u66f4\u4f4e\u90e8\u7f72\u6210\u672c\u4fa7\u7684 Pareto \u524d\u6cbf\u3002",
