research/history/logs/agent_action_0218.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"248"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此兼容性为直接兼容。r214-r217 已连续证明在 EF=1 下沿 K 轴增加查表预算能稳定压低 <0.5x 区域的 FVU，且最近一轮 K=240 仍把最佳低开销 FVU 压到 0.1483，说明边际收益虽变小但尚未消失；因此本轮继续只提升 K 到 248，目标是在总成本仍预计略低于 0.5x、继续留在低开销区的前提下，再验证 topk@EF1 的贴边收益，并避免直接跳到可能越过 0.5x 的更大 K。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@EF1,K248 仍有可见改善且运行代价稳定，则可再补一个贴近 0.5x 的终点。","如果 K248 的收益已经很小或训练代价恶化，则说明 EF=1 下继续堆 K 基本到头，后续应转向新的低成本 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 仍是当前 <0.5x 区域最稳的直接兼容主线，导出路径最简单，且连续数轮都给出可解释的 Pareto 改善。","选择 K=248 而不是 256，是为了尽量稳妥地继续停留在 <0.5x 区域，同时测试贴边预算下的最后一段边际收益。","评估时继续同步比较 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认这段额外查表预算是否值得。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮保持单一变化轴并延续已验证有效的低开销 topk 主线。相比直接冲 K=256，K=248 更符合当前“补 <0.5x 前沿”而不是跨到 0.5x 以上质量锚点的目标；风险是收益可能已接近饱和，但这正是当前需要测清的信号。","summary":"继续使用直接兼容的 topk family，固定 EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，把 K 提到 248，测试是否能在仍低于 0.5x 总成本的前提下，把低开销区最佳 FVU 从 0.1483 进一步压低。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0077.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Rounds 75 and 76 ruled out the simplest matched single-stage alternatives under the current `two_stage_residual` anchor: both `topk` and `jumprelu` were clearly worse at `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=2.0e-3`. The next single matched architecture probe should therefore test a structurally different exportable decomposition rather than another plain selector. `codebook_topk` is the highest-value remaining yes/no probe because it still maps to a finite weighted sum over static vector libraries, but may reduce LUTurbo online coefficient and lookup cost by reusing a compact static basis instead of a full staged residual path. This round asks one question only: under the exact current mainline recipe, is `codebook_topk` competitive enough in full-curve behavior to remain worth later consideration, or should it be ruled out as clearly inferior to `two_stage_residual`?","summary":"Use the one allowed matched architecture probe on `codebook_topk`. Keep the current mainline recipe fixed at `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and the same aux/runtime settings, and change only `ARCHITECTURE` from `two_stage_residual` to `codebook_topk`. Judge the run by the whole trajectory, not just the endpoint: if `codebook_topk` stays reasonably close with a healthy curve, keep it in reserve because its shared-codebook structure may lower LUTurbo online lookup and coefficient cost; if it is clearly worse throughout, close the probe and return to the `two_stage_residual` mainline next round.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"codebook_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This obeys the Round 77 rule by changing exactly one primary variable, `architecture`, while keeping `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, `LR`, and the rest of the recipe fixed. `codebook_topk` is a better use of the single probe than revisiting already-rejected plain selector variants because it tests a different cost-quality tradeoff that is still compatible with LUTurbo's static export contract. The main risk is that prior matched probing in an earlier regime already suggested weakness, but this remains the most informative remaining architecture-worthiness check under the current mainline anchor.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"codebook_topk"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 77 spends the single allowed matched architecture probe on `codebook_topk` against the current `two_stage_residual` mainline recipe, because it represents a distinct static-library decomposition that may reduce LUTurbo online lookup and coefficient cost while preserving exportability.","Judge this probe as a family-worthiness test only: compare matched `codebook_topk@128` against the `two_stage_residual` reference at fixed `EF=12`, `signum`, and `LR=2.0e-3`, then return to the `two_stage_residual` mainline next round regardless of outcome."],"next_hypotheses":["If matched `codebook_topk` is reasonably close with a healthy curve, return to the `two_stage_residual` mainline next round but keep one later `codebook_topk` revisit available because its shared-codebook path may be cheaper to deploy.","If matched `codebook_topk` is clearly worse than `two_stage_residual` across the curve, close the probe and return to the `two_stage_residual` mainline next round.","If matched `codebook_topk` unexpectedly beats the current `two_stage_residual` reference, still return to the `two_stage_residual` mainline next round per policy, but record `codebook_topk` as a high-priority later follow-up family."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0239.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"48"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"frontier_mapping","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，部署侧仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 reference_round=r238 只改一个 env 参数 `K=48`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=topk`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=signum`、`LR=0.003`、`AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125` 及其余配置不变，测试在约 0.30x 总成本处，是否能把刚建立的左端点 `topk@K32` 的 FVU=0.3199 继续明显压低，并补出 `0.28x -> 0.31x` 之间缺失的 Pareto 过渡点。选择这一步而不是继续开新 family，是因为 r238 已证明最简单单库结构在超低 K 左端优于 `factorized_topk@0.30x`，当前最高信息量问题变成 topk 左侧前沿的真实斜率，而不是再次切到最近已给出负信号的 `codebook_topk`、`factorized_topk` 或 recipe 微调线。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `topk@EF1,K48` 在约 0.30x 成本处显著优于 `K32`，且 `tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens` 没有明显恶化，则相对本轮继续单变量上探到 `K=56` 或直接回接 `K=64`，把左侧低成本前沿补完整。","如果 `K48` 相比 `K32` 改善很小，则说明 `<0.3x` 左端的单库 topk 已接近明显退化区，后续主注意力应回到更高价值的 `0.31x-0.49x` 区间。","如果质量改善存在但运行显著更慢，则按运行时优先级将其记为负面系统信号，不把该配方升格为左侧前沿点。"],"notes_to_memory":["r238 已确认 `topk@EF1,K32` 在约 0.28x 成本处优于当前最左端 `factorized_topk@0.30x`，说明左侧超低成本前沿应由 plain topk 而不是 factorized scorer 主导。","当前 `<0.5x` 前沿在 `0.28x` 与 `0.31x` 之间仍有空档；相对 r238 只提升 `K` 是最小、最可解释、最有利于刻画左端 Pareto 斜率的动作。","评估本轮必须同时比较 `val_fvu`、`tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens`；若只是小幅质量改善但运行明显更慢，应直接视为负面信号。"],"reference_round":238,"self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r238 只改 `K`，不联动 architecture、EF、LR、optimizer、AUXK_ALPHA 或任何新参数。主要风险是 `K32->48` 的收益可能不足以形成新的非支配点；但在左端低成本区刚出现正信号后，先补中间过渡点比贸然切回已被证伪的 family 更符合当前 Pareto 补全目标。","summary":"相对 r238 的 `topk@EF1,K32` 做一次严格 param_only 左端补点，仅设置 `K=48`，验证 plain topk 能否在约 0.30x 总成本处继续压低 FVU，并补完整个超低成本左侧前沿。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0020.json:7:  "family_name": "topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0020.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Round 19 showed that `topk/signum/LR=1.6e-3/EF=12` at `K=8` suffered a large quality drop and much heavier dead-feature pressure, with the late curve nearly flattening but not fully collapsing. This round changes only `K`, moving from `8` to `4`, to answer the single remaining boundary question: whether the current export-compatible topk recipe has any usable signal left at the absolute minimum allowed K, or whether `K=8` already marks the effective floor.",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0020.json:20:    "summary": "Finish the current low-K boundary sweep on the active topk mainline: keep `ARCHITECTURE=topk`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and reduce `K` from `8` to `4` to locate the hard lower bound of the present topk/signum regime.",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0020.json:23:    "family_name": "topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0020.json:25:    "self_review": "This stays on the active `topk` family, changes exactly one primary variable (`k`), respects the fixed `EF=12` rule and allowed-K set, and closes the current K-only frontier scan cleanly. The main risk is that `K=4` may be clearly past the useful regime, but `command=\"stop\"` is disallowed and this is the most informative remaining single-variable question because it determines whether `K=8` is merely weak or already beyond the practical floor.",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0020.json:30:        "value": "topk"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0020.json:53:      "Even though the late curve nearly flattened at `K=8`, it did not fully collapse, so running `K=4` is the cleanest way to locate the hard lower boundary of the current topk/signum/EF12 recipe."
