research/history/round_summaries/round_0214.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family: topk\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d {b_i} \u6765\u81ea\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ea\u505a\u5355\u6837\u672c top-k \u9009\u62e9\u4e0e\u7cfb\u6570\u8ba1\u7b97\uff0c\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u65f6\u4ecd\u662f\u5355\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u5f53\u524d <0.5x \u533a\u57df\u53ea\u6709 topk@K64,EF1 \u8fd9\u4e00\u4e2a\u70b9\uff0c\u4e14\u5b83\u5df2\u7ecf\u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e\u540c\u6210\u672c\u9644\u8fd1\u7684 factorized_topk\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u672c\u8f6e\u4e0d\u518d\u7ee7\u7eed\u7ea0\u7f20 lowrank_factorized_residual \u7684 param_only policy \u7ec6\u8282\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u5230\u6700\u7a33\u7684\u4f4e\u5f00\u9500\u5355\u5e93 family\uff0c\u5728 EF=1 \u4fdd\u6301 encoder \u6210\u672c\u7ea6 0.25x \u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u628a K \u63d0\u5230 128\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u603b\u6210\u672c\u4ecd\u7ea6 0.37x\u3001\u660e\u663e\u4f4e\u4e8e 0.5x \u7684\u6761\u4ef6\u4e0b\uff0c\u628a FVU \u4ece 0.2583 \u663e\u8457\u538b\u4f4e\uff0c\u8865\u51fa\u7b2c\u4e8c\u4e2a\u771f\u6b63\u6709\u4ef7\u503c\u7684 <0.5x Pareto \u70b9\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0214.json:20:    "summary": "\u5207\u56de\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u7684 topk family\uff0c\u56fa\u5b9a EF=1\u3001signum\u3001LR=3e-3\uff0c\u53ea\u628a\u4f4e\u5f00\u9500\u5355\u5e93\u8def\u7ebf\u7684\u652f\u6301\u89c4\u6a21\u62c9\u5230 K=128\uff0c\u76ee\u6807\u662f\u5728\u4ecd\u4f4e\u4e8e 0.5x \u603b\u6210\u672c\u7684\u6761\u4ef6\u4e0b\uff0c\u8865\u51fa\u4e00\u4e2a\u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d 0.31x \u70b9\u7684\u65b0 <0.5x Pareto \u5019\u9009\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0214.json:23:    "family_name": "topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0214.json:47:      "topk \u7684\u5bfc\u51fa\u5f62\u5f0f\u6700\u5e72\u51c0\uff1a\u5355\u9759\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9 LUTurbo\uff0c\u4e14\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u552f\u4e00\u5df2\u8fdb\u5165 <0.5x frontier \u7684 family\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0214.json:48:      "r207/r208 \u5df2\u8868\u660e\u5728\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u533a topk \u660e\u663e\u5f3a\u4e8e factorized_topk\uff0c\u4f46\u76ee\u524d\u7f3a\u5c11\u540c family \u5728 <0.5x \u533a\u57df\u5185\u66f4\u9ad8 K \u7684\u8d28\u91cf\u66f2\u7ebf\u70b9\uff1b\u672c\u8f6e\u4f18\u5148\u8865\u8fd9\u6761\u6700\u77ed\u94fe\u8def\u524d\u6cbf\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0214.json:52:      "\u5982\u679c topk@EF1,K128 \u5728 <0.5x \u5185\u663e\u8457\u4f18\u4e8e K64 \u4e14\u541e\u5410\u4e0b\u964d\u53ef\u63a5\u53d7\uff0c\u5219\u518d\u56de\u5230\u540c family \u53ea\u6cbf K \u8f74\u8865\u4e00\u4e2a\u4e2d\u95f4\u70b9\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0214.json:64:    "architecture": "topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0214.json:73:    "description": "\u5207\u56de\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u7684 topk family\uff0c\u56fa\u5b9a EF=1\u3001signum\u3001LR=3e-3\uff0c\u53ea\u628a\u4f4e\u5f00\u9500\u5355\u5e93\u8def\u7ebf\u7684\u652f\u6301\u89c4\u6a21\u62c9\u5230 K=128\uff0c\u76ee\u6807\u662f\u5728\u4ecd\u4f4e\u4e8e 0.5x \u603b\u6210\u672c\u7684\u6761\u4ef6\u4e0b\uff0c\u8865\u51fa\u4e00\u4e2a\u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d 0.31x \u70b9\u7684\u65b0 <0.5x Pareto \u5019\u9009\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是 trunk 静态向量库、{b_i} 是 residual 静态向量库；factorized residual scorer 只影响在线选择与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端导出形态，因此可直接落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。基于 r210 已证明该 family 在 K=64、EF=1 下能以 0.69x 拿到 0.1256 FVU，当前主矛盾是 trunk 成本过高而不是训练质量不足；本轮严格锚定 r210，只改一个主轴 TRUNK_RANK，从 auto≈256 下调到 32，测试是否能把 total_cost 明确压入 <0.5x 区域，同时尽量保留明显优于同成本 topk 的 FVU。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:25:    "self_review": "该提案满足单变量原则：相对 r210 只改 TRUNK_RANK，其余核心配方保持不变。选择 32 而不是 16，是因为它仍应明显低于 0.5x，同时比更激进的 trunk 压缩更有机会保住 r210 展现出的质量优势；主要风险是 trunk 过窄后 coarse 补偿能力不足，FVU 可能回落到接近 topk。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:60:      "如果 TRUNK_RANK=32 仍明显优于 <0.5x 区域 topk 前沿，则继续相对本轮单变量下探 TRUNK_RANK=16，检查成本-质量拐点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:61:      "如果 TRUNK_RANK=32 的 FVU 退化过大，则保留 r210 作为质量锚点，转向同 family 的单变量 K 轴或回到 topk 前沿继续补点。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:83:    "self_review": "该提案满足单变量原则：相对 r210 只改 TRUNK_RANK，其余核心配方保持不变。选择 32 而不是 16，是因为它仍应明显低于 0.5x，同时比更激进的 trunk 压缩更有机会保住 r210 展现出的质量优势；主要风险是 trunk 过窄后 coarse 补偿能力不足，FVU 可能回落到接近 topk。",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0144.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"confirm_baseline","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 静态库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。经过 r141-r143 的 matched architecture probes 后，当前已经重新确认 two-stage soft-codebook 主线在质量上显著优于 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual、lowrank_residual 与 factorized_topk，但这些 probe 的总耗时更短，说明近期运行代价结论可能混杂了架构差异而非主线 recipe 漂移。本轮只回答一个问题：回到主线参考配方 ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 做一次 clean baseline 复验，当前 feasible 主线的 FVU、训练曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens 是否仍稳定可复现，从而为后续继续做主线 recipe 调整提供干净锚点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 clean baseline 继续稳定复现 0.0581 附近且运行代价正常，则下一轮继续留在主线 family，优先做一个单变量 recipe 问题而不是继续开 architecture probe。","若 clean baseline 的吞吐或总耗时明显恶化而 FVU 不变，则优先把这视为运行时信号，而不是误判为主线架构退化。","若 clean baseline 本身出现曲线漂移或终点退化，则先重新建立主线锚点，再决定是否进入 LR 或成本轴。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 仍是当前兼容 frontier 上质量最强的可行主线，导出形式未变，继续属于扩展兼容。","r141-r143 三个 matched architecture probes 已把更简化候选的质量下界看清：单阶段 soft-codebook、plain lowrank residual、factorized_topk 都未超过当前主线。","在 probe 轮次后先补 clean baseline，有助于分离架构差异与近期运行代价波动，避免后续 recipe 归因失真。"],"primary_variable":"clean_baseline","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：本轮不新开 family，不改 K、EF、optimizer、LR，也不混入额外成本轴或 loss 轴变量，只做主线 clean baseline 复验。该动作符合当前推荐顺序：EF 已确认在预算内，且经过连续架构探针后，先恢复可信主线锚点比直接继续调 recipe 更稳。风险是这一轮可能再次得到与现有主线相同的 FVU，但它能提供必要的运行代价参照，避免把架构探针的更短时长误读为主线 recipe 问题。","summary":"回到当前主线参考配方做一次 clean baseline 复验：固定 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3，不引入任何新结构或新 recipe，只确认当前 feasible 主线的 FVU、训练曲线与运行代价是否仍稳定可复现。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0064.json:7:  "family_name": "codebook_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0064.json:19:    "hypothesis": "With the `gated` mainline stalled for eleven rounds and the lighter selector probes `group_topk` and `bucketed_topk` both coming back clearly worse, the next highest-value matched architecture probe is `codebook_topk`: it remains LUTurbo-compatible because the reconstruction is still a finite sum over static libraries, but it changes the architecture by adding a hard coarse codebook selection before the sparse residual. This round answers one question only: under the matched `K=128`, `signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `EF=12` recipe, is `codebook_topk` intrinsically strong enough to justify any later follow-up, or should it be ruled out immediately.",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0064.json:20:    "summary": "Run one matched architecture probe by switching `ARCHITECTURE` from `gated` to `codebook_topk` while keeping `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed.",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0064.json:23:    "family_name": "codebook_topk",
