research/history/logs/agent_action_0205.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_topk"},{"key":"K","value":"32"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"smaller_k","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: factorized_topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 b_i 来自单个静态向量库；factorized scorer 仅用于在线打分与选址，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单库查表加权求和，因此属于直接兼容。基于 r204 已在 K=64、EF=2 下拿到 0.44x / 0.3013 的 <0.5x 点，本轮继续保持 architecture、EF、optimizer、LR 不变，仅将 K 从 64 下探到 32，预计 deployment cost 可由约 0.06x 进一步降到约 0.03x，使 total_cost 约落在 0.41x，补全更低成本端覆盖，并检验该 family 在更短查表链路下的 FVU 退化斜率。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 K=32 仍保持可接受 FVU，可继续在 factorized_topk 上单变量下探 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM，争取把 encoder cost 也往下压。","如果 K=32 的 FVU 退化过大，则保留 K=64 作为 <0.5x 主点，并转去 topk 或 lowrank_residual 的低成本对照以补前沿形状。"],"notes_to_memory":["factorized_topk 在 LUTurbo 链路中可直接导出为单静态字典的 top-k 查表加权和，兼容性稳定，不因 scorer factorization 改变 decoder 形式。","本轮继续只改 K，沿 deployment 成本轴下探，避免把 encoder 降本与 lookup 降本混在一起。"],"primary_variable":"k","self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则，目标明确指向 <0.5x 区域扩点。主要风险是 K=32 可能把 FVU 推高过快，但这正是当前低开销 regime 需要量化的 tradeoff。","summary":"在直接兼容 family factorized_topk 上做单变量低开销下探：固定 EF=2、signum、LR=3e-3，仅把 K 从 64 降到 32，目标是把 total_cost 从 0.44x 进一步压到约 0.41x，并补全 <0.5x Pareto 前沿的更低部署成本端。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0225.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"候选 family: jumprelu。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；JumpReLU 只改变单样本在线侧的阈值化支持形成与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端的单库有限加权和形式，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。r223 已确认 `topk@EF1,K248` 的向上 LR 分支没有收益，r224 也确认 lowrank_factorized_residual 的 scorer 压缩在 <0.5x 目标区仍落后于同成本 topk；因此当前最有信息量的下一步，不是继续清洗已饱和 family 的 recipe，而是在不增加 total_cost 的前提下测试新的同成本 selector 机制。严格锚定 r222，只改一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE=jumprelu`，保留 `EF=1,K=248,signum,LR=3.0e-3,AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 不变，验证 learned-threshold 支持塑形能否在相同 `total_cost≈0.49x` 下，把 <0.5x 区域 FVU 压到当前 topk 最佳 0.1462 以下，或者至少给出比 topk 更有希望的曲线形状而不拖慢训练。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `jumprelu@EF1,K248` 在相同 0.49x 成本下优于 `topk@K248` 的 FVU=0.1462，且 tokens_per_sec / duration_sec 没有明显恶化，则下一轮基于本轮做一次 clean repeat，确认它是否能成为新的 <0.5x 直接兼容锚点。","如果 `jumprelu` 与 topk 质量接近但运行代价更差，则将其仅记录为历史参考，不继续占用低开销主线轮次。","如果 `jumprelu` 明显差于 topk，则关闭这条 plain-selector thresholding 支线，下一轮转向另一条同成本或近邻成本的新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 `selection_cost_estimate()` 显示 `jumprelu@EF1,K248` 与 `topk@EF1,K248` 的 combined_ratio 同为约 0.49x，因此这是一次纯 selector 机制比较，而不是成本变化导致的混杂实验。","r223 与 r224 分别对 topk recipe 继续清洗、以及 lowrank_factorized_residual scorer 压缩给出负面信号；当前应优先测试新的同成本 family，而不是继续沿这两条线做局部小修。","`jumprelu` 保持单静态库导出契约，属于直接兼容 family；若它也失败，则说明当前 <0.5x 区域里 plain single-library selector 的主导瓶颈更可能是表示容量而非支持塑形规则。"],"reference_round":222,"self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则：相对有效参考轮 r222 只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 一个 env 参数，K、EF、optimizer、LR、AUXK_ALPHA 和所有运行时参数全部保持不变。选择 `jumprelu` 而不是继续回到 topk/group_topk，是因为它在历史上虽未成为主线，但比纯 grouped 竞争更接近“同成本下改变支持塑形”的独立问题，同时不会额外抬高部署或选择成本。","summary":"相对 r222 的 `topk@EF1,K248,AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 做一次严格 param_only architecture probe，仅切换到 `jumprelu`，测试在相同 0.49x 成本下，阈值化支持塑形是否能把 <0.5x 前沿继续压低。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0233.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r u_r + Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是静态 trunk 向量库、{b_i} 是静态 sparse residual 向量库；在线侧先用低秩 trunk 分支给出低维主成分重构，再对剩余残差做有限个静态 residual 向量的加权和，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路：trunk 分支作为一组固定库项查表求和，residual 分支作为第二组固定库项查表求和，最终两支线性相加，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。相对 r210 只改一个 env 参数 `K=32`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_factorized_residual`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`signum`、`LR=0.003` 及其余配置不变，测试是否能把当前已验证可行的 `lowrank_factorized_residual@K64` 从约 0.69x 总成本进一步压到约 0.66x 左右，同时仍显著优于 `<0.5x` 区域 topk 前沿的 FVU。选择这一步的原因是：r232 已经说明继续上探 `JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD` 只带来更差 FVU 与更长时长，阈值初始化线应当关闭；而当前剩余低成本新 family 中，`factorized_topk`、`group_topk` 已被证伪，`adaptive_budget_topk` 在 batch_size=1 下退化为普通 topk，`gated/routed/whitened/codebook/two_stage` 与大多数低秩残差变体在 EF=1 下都超预算。此时最有价值的动作不是再做一个高概率无效的新 family probe，而是把唯一仍可行、且质量明显优于 plain topk 的低秩残差主线沿 K 轴向低开销方向拉近，补一枚 0.5x-0.7x 过渡锚点。","summary":"相对 r210 的 `lowrank_factorized_residual@EF1,K64` 做一次严格 param_only 的部署成本下探，仅设置 `K=32`。目标不是刷新全局最低 FVU，而是把当前少数仍具质量优势且满足预算的扩展兼容 family 向更低成本侧推进，补一枚靠近 `<0.5x` 区域的过渡 Pareto/anchor 点。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"information_gain","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：相对参考轮 r210 只改 `K`，不联动 architecture、EF、LR、optimizer 或任何新增 knob。虽然当前策略强调 `<0.5x` 主战场，但经过最近数轮验证，真正留在该区间且仍未退化为无信息 probe 的新 family 已非常少；继续在已证伪的 `factorized_topk/group_topk` 或已显著走弱的 `jumprelu threshold-init` 线上消耗轮次，信息收益更低。把 `lowrank_factorized_residual` 从 K64 向 K32 下压，是一个清晰的“过渡锚点”动作：它不违背低开销探索主旨，同时能检验该 family 是否能沿部署成本轴继续向 `<0.5x` 方向逼近。主要风险是 K 减半后 residual 容量不足，FVU 明显回退；但这正是本轮需要以最小改动确认的关键问题。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"32"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r232 已确认继续上探 `JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD` 不是正收益：FVU 从 r227 的 0.14564 回退到 0.14595，且总时长上升到 489s，因此应关闭这条阈值初始化线。","在 EF=1 的当前预算下，低秩残差系里只有 `lowrank_factorized_residual` 仍稳定满足成本硬约束；`lowrank_residual/jumprelu_residual/grouped_residual/soft_codebook` 都已超 budget，不适合当前默认动作。","`lowrank_factorized_residual@K64` 已给出 0.69x / FVU 0.1256 的高质量过渡点；本轮的核心问题是它沿 K 轴下探时，是否还能保住足够多的质量优势，而不是继续围绕已证伪的 plain-selector 变体做小修小补。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_factorized_residual@K32` 仍显著优于 `topk@K248` 的 FVU=0.1462，且 tokens_per_sec、duration_sec 保持接近 r210，则可继续相对本轮单变量下探到 `K=16`，测试这条扩展兼容低秩残差线能否进一步逼近 `<0.5x` 入口。","如果 `K=32` 的 FVU 只小幅回退但仍明显优于同预算附近的 plain topk，则将其保留为 0.5x-0.7x 区间的高价值过渡锚点，并停止在 plain single-library selector 上继续过密搜索。","如果 `K=32` 质量明显塌陷，说明该 family 当前优势高度依赖较高 residual lookup 预算；则关闭其向更低 K 的继续下探，把注意力转回真正新的兼容结构或其他更轻的多库方案。"],"reference_round":210}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0163.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库上的固定向量，alpha_i 是单样本门控后选出的稀疏系数，因此最终表示是单静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为直接兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 1.0x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，且仍低于当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的约 1.25x。本轮严格保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 与主要 recipe 不变，只将 architecture 从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 改为 gated，回答唯一问题：在当前低 EF 可部署 regime 下，增加简单门控是否足以让单库路线更接近主线质量，还是它仍会明显落后于带 trunk、soft-codebook 和 staged refinement 的主线结构。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 gated 明显落后于当前主线，则说明简单门控单库路线在当前 regime 下不值得继续，下一轮回到主线。","若 gated 与当前主线差距小于预期且运行代价更优，则记录其为低成本直接兼容备选，但下一轮仍按要求回到主线。","若 gated 意外优于当前主线，则说明当前主线 family 的系统级收益需要重新审视，但本轮仅做架构价值判断，不连续展开新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["gated 满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性为直接兼容。","本轮严格是 matched architecture probe：EF、K、optimizer、LR 与主要 recipe 全部固定，只改 architecture。","r159-r162 已覆盖 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual、lowrank_residual、factorized_topk、topk；本轮补充 gated 这一剩余可行直接兼容低成本路线。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把质量差异与吞吐波动混淆。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮遵守架构探针规则，只改一个主变量 architecture，并保持主线的 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变。选择 gated 是因为它是当前尚未在这一严格 matched 配方下补齐的可行直接兼容单库对照，能回答简单门控是否足以弥补纯 topk 路线表达不足这一剩余问题。","summary":"插入一个严格匹配的架构探针：将当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 替换为 gated，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断这种简单门控的直接兼容单库架构是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0089.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual`, `lowrank_residual_vq`, `lowrank_jumprelu_residual`, `lowrank_gated_residual`, and `lowrank_grouped_residual` all failed to challenge the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128 anchor, the most informative remaining matched architecture probe is the plain `lowrank_residual` family. It preserves the same low-rank trunk and static-library weighted-sum export path while removing the extra second residual stage and auxiliary selector structure, making it the cleanest test of whether the current mainline's quality advantage truly requires two-stage residual allocation. If `lowrank_residual` is still clearly weaker under the exact matched `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe, then the simpler single-stage low-rank family is not worth continuing in the current LUTurbo-aligned regime.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe by switching `ARCHITECTURE` to `lowrank_residual` while keeping `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"lowrank_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This obeys the matched architecture probe rule by changing only `architecture` and keeping the mainline `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe fixed. `lowrank_residual` is the strongest remaining LUTurbo-aligned probe because it is the simplest low-rank static-library decomposition still comparable to the current mainline, and it directly tests whether the second residual pass is buying necessary quality or only extra online cost. The main risk is that the family may underfit badly at matched K128, but that negative result would still answer the exact worth-continuing question cleanly.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 89 spends the single allowed matched architecture probe on `lowrank_residual` against the exact `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128/EF12/signum/LR=2.0e-3 anchor.","Judge this run strictly as a family-worthiness test for the simplest low-rank single-stage residual decomposition; the core question is whether dropping the second residual stage can preserve enough quality to justify the lower expected online cost.","Return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round regardless of outcome; do not chain another new-family probe immediately after this one."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_residual` is clearly weaker than the matched `lowrank_two_stage_residual` anchor, discard it and resume mainline tuning on `lowrank_two_stage_residual` next round.","If `lowrank_residual` is unexpectedly competitive at matched K128, record it as a viable lower-cost branch but still return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round per probe policy."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0065.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"With the `gated` mainline stalled for twelve rounds and recent single-stage selector probes (`group_topk`, `bucketed_topk`, `codebook_topk`) all failing to beat it, the next highest-value matched architecture probe is `two_stage_residual`: it remains LUTurbo-compatible because the reconstruction is still a finite weighted sum over static libraries, but distributes the fixed `K=128` budget across two sequential residual passes. This round answers one question only: under the matched `signum`/`LR=2.0e-3`/`EF=12` recipe, is that staged residual decomposition intrinsically strong enough to justify any later follow-up, or should it be ruled out immediately.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe by switching `ARCHITECTURE` from `gated` to `two_stage_residual` while keeping `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"two_stage_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This obeys the Round 65 policy by changing exactly one primary variable: architecture. `two_stage_residual` is a more informative remaining probe than batch-coupled top-k variants because it stays single-sample deployable, and it tests a distinct multi-stage static-library decomposition that is closer to LUTurbo's lookup-plus-selective-compensation execution model than another small selector tweak.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 65 spends the single allowed matched architecture probe on `two_stage_residual` after recent single-stage selector variants all underperformed matched `gated`.","`two_stage_residual` is extended-compatible with LUTurbo because its final reconstruction can be exported as the sum of two fixed-size sparse weighted sums over static decoder libraries, with a fixed stage split of the total `K`.","Judge this probe strictly as a family-worthiness test against matched `gated` K128: if it is clearly worse, discard it and return to the `gated` mainline next round; if it is competitive, record the result but still return to the mainline per policy."],"next_hypotheses":["If `two_stage_residual` is clearly worse than matched `gated`, discard the family and return to the `gated` mainline next round.","If `two_stage_residual` is roughly competitive, record it as a possible staged lookup-plus-compensation direction but still return to the `gated` mainline next round per policy.","If `two_stage_residual` unexpectedly beats matched `gated`, schedule at most one later follow-up after the mandated return to the `gated` mainline."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0204.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_topk"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"smaller_k","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: factorized_topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 b_i 来自单个静态向量库，低秩 factor scorer 只参与在线选择、不改变 decoder 形式，因此对 LUTurbo/Lottable 属于直接兼容。单主变量选择 k：把当前 0.50x 前沿点 factorized_topk 从 K=128 下调到 K=64，保持 ARCHITECTURE/EF/OPT/LR 不变，可把 deployment cost 约从 0.12x 降到 0.06x，使 total_cost 约从 0.50x 降到 0.44x，直接补到 <0.5x 区域；预期 FVU 会升高，但仍可能成为该低开销区域的首个有效 Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 K=64 成功占住 <0.5x 前沿，再继续沿同一 family 单变量下探 K=32。","如果 K=64 的 FVU 退化过大，再回到 factorized_topk 固定 K=64，单变量下调 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM 以继续压 encoder 成本，或转向 topk/EF=1 做更低成本锚点。"],"notes_to_memory":["factorized_topk 的 decoder 仍是单静态字典加权和，属于直接兼容 family，可继续作为 <0.5x 区域主力低成本基线。","本轮只改 K，避免把 architecture/EF/LR 混入，便于归因低开销前沿是否主要受 lookup 成本驱动。"],"primary_variable":"k","self_review":"方案严格遵守单变量原则，且不需要改 sparsify/ 代码。主要风险是 K=64 的 FVU 可能明显差于现有 0.50x 点；但当前任务优先级是补 <0.5x 覆盖，这个风险是可接受的。","summary":"运行一个纯参数低开销探索：保持 factorized_topk, EF=2, signum, LR=3e-3 不变，仅将 K 从 128 降到 64，目标是在直接兼容前提下把 total_cost 压到约 0.44x，并为 <0.5x 区域建立首个可行 Pareto 候选。","touched_files":[]}
