research/history/logs/agent_action_0179.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_jumprelu_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_jumprelu_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` under the unchanged mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3.0e-3`). Final reconstruction is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk and the JumpReLU selector only changes which residual dictionary atoms `b_i` are activated and their coefficients. This is `扩展兼容`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export the trunk factors and residual dictionary as static vector libraries, then execute `trunk lookup + thresholded sparse selection + weighted lookup-sum` online. The probe asks one question only: in the low-EF feasible regime, does learned thresholding provide a better architecture tradeoff than the current soft-codebook two-stage mainline, or should this family be ruled out. Encoder selection cost should stay in the feasible band at `EF=2`, so this should produce a real signal instead of a policy reject.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune exactly one cost knob such as `TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`.","If `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` underperforms the mainline on FVU or shows materially worse `tokens_per_sec`/runtime without compensating benefit, mark the family as not worth continuing in the low-cost regime."],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_jumprelu_residual` is LUTurbo `扩展兼容`: decode remains a finite weighted sum over a static low-rank trunk plus a static residual dictionary; JumpReLU only changes selector-side activation sparsity.","This matched probe stays inside the likely feasible encoder-cost regime and is more informative than another routed/bucketed-style over-budget probe.","When scoring the run, inspect `tokens_per_sec`, wall-clock time, and `final_total_tokens` together with FVU; a tiny quality gain with slower training is a negative signal."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes while `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` remain fixed to the mainline recipe. This probe avoids another likely budget rejection and tests a remaining compatible architecture that can still deliver a clean go/no-go answer for the low-EF frontier.","summary":"Probe `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` as the one matched architecture change. It is LUTurbo-exportable (`扩展兼容`) through a static low-rank trunk plus static residual dictionary, and it should give a real low-cost signal on whether learned thresholding is worth continuing versus the current soft-codebook two-stage mainline.","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0236.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"LR","value":"0.0027"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，部署侧仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 reference_round=r223 只改一个 env 参数 `LR=0.0027`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=topk`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`K=248`、`OPTIMIZER=signum`、`AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 及其余配置不变，测试在约 0.49x 总成本、当前最强 `<0.5x` 低开销锚点上，略微收缩 signum 步长能否改善 late-stage 收敛，把 FVU 压到低于 0.14621。选择这一步而不是继续推进 `jumprelu` 或 `codebook_topk`，是因为 r234 已给出“极小质量收益伴随异常总时长”的负面系统信号，而 r235 则在约 0.38x 处同时暴露出明显更差质量与更长总时长；在最近新 family 连续不给正信号的情况下，回到最短选择链路、最强低成本直兼容锚点做一次对称的保守 LR probe，信息价值更高且归因更干净。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `topk@EF1,K248,LR=0.0027` 继续降低 FVU，且 `tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens` 没有明显恶化，则相对本轮继续做一次严格 param_only clean repeat，确认这是否是 `<0.5x` 区域新的默认锚点。","如果 FVU 基本持平或回退，则关闭 `topk@K248` 的 LR 微调线，结论回到 `LR=0.003` 已是当前低开销 topk 主线的更合理设置。","如果质量小幅改善但运行明显更慢，则按运行时优先级将其记为负面系统信号，不把该配方升格为主线前沿点。"],"notes_to_memory":["r234 的 `jumprelu@K248,bandwidth=0.025` 虽把 FVU 压到 0.14545，但总时长升到 899s，应视为明显负面系统信号；后续不宜继续在该线做密集微调。","r235 的 `codebook_topk@K32` 在约 0.38x 成本处给出 FVU=0.3161，且总时长 628s，说明单 coarse codebook 低成本线当前实现没有形成可用前沿。","在最近新 family 连续失利后，当前更高信息量的问题是：当前最强 `<0.5x` 直兼容锚点是否仍有纯 recipe 侧的小幅可压缩空间，而不是继续开启更复杂但大概率无效的新结构。","评估本轮必须同时比较 `val_fvu`、`tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens`；若只是极小质量变化但运行更慢，应直接视为负面信号。"],"reference_round":223,"self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r223 只改 `LR`，不联动 architecture、K、EF、optimizer、AUXK_ALPHA 或任何新参数。主要风险是把步长降到 `0.0027` 后在固定 token 预算内反而收敛不足；但在 `0.0036` 已被证明偏激进、而多个新 low-cost family 又连续失利的背景下，这是当前最小、最可解释、且完全留在 `<0.5x` 主战区内的下一步。","summary":"相对 r223 的 `topk@EF1,K248` 做一次严格 param_only 保守步长 probe，仅设置 `LR=0.0027`，验证当前最强 `<0.5x` 直兼容锚点是否还能在不改变成本的前提下继续压低 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
